# init(multiPolygon:)

**Initializer**

Creates and returns a renderer that handles drawing for the specified multipolygon overlay object.

## Declaration

```swift
init(multiPolygon: MKMultiPolygon)
```

## Parameters

- **multiPolygon**: An [doc://com.apple.mapkit/documentation/MapKit/MKMultiPolygon] to initialize the renderer with.
